title: DC59: A sneak peak at what sets Dyson's cordless apart - Official Dyson Video
description: Powered by the V6 Dyson digital motor, The Dyson DC59 vacuum cleaner delivers high suction and powerful pick-up. Without the hassle of a cord. #cutthecord

transcripts: So because we have the Dyson digital motor V6 as the heart of the machine that translates to really good suction down at the cleaner head where we're picking up dust from the floor. So if I switch this machine on, we've got fantastically high suction especially compared with other cordless machines. And that really shows when you start doing comparative tests looking at how well it picks up on hard floors against other cordless machines and even some corded machines It's leaving loads behind as well. Much better
